{"tid":2365215,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"逾 900 公頃官地解凍建丁屋？","createTime":"2021-01-13T14:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T14:24:28.000Z","uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e6c2968138715612463cd877ec3702a363368948","tid":2365215,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T14:24:28.000Z","msg":"官地（私人協約）或換地方式建丁屋的政策，前年在高等法院原訟庭被裁定違憲政府原本約 930 公頃預留丁屋的官地變相「凍結」，但政府及新界鄉議局今日上訴得直，有關官地或會「解凍」？本土研究社成員黃肇鴻相信，有關用地將繼續予原居民建丁屋，未能釋放建造公屋或私人樓宇；房委會委員、民主黨尹兆堅形容，裁決形同加固「金剛圈」，「唔駛諗嗰 900 幾公頃鄉村式發展土地啦，全部被箍住哂」。<br />\n<br />\n發展局回覆指出，會研究上訴庭判詞，安排恢復接收、處理申請官地（私人協約）或換地方式的丁屋申請。<br />\n<br />\n相關報道：<br />\n<br />\n私人協約、換地建丁屋被裁定違憲　政府及新界鄉議局上訴得直<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XE8PE1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XE8PE1&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuO4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=58fb0991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XE8PE1</a><br />\n<br />\n【丁屋覆核案】鄉議局上訴全勝　劉業強：今次係贏 3 比 0　籲盡快恢官地建丁屋<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3bAU2SM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3bAU2SM&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuO4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=55e224b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3bAU2SM</a><br />\n<br />\n【丁屋覆核案】逾 900 公頃官地解凍建丁屋？　本土研：本有望建公屋居屋　發展局：將恢復申請<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3nFFDqK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3nFFDqK&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuO4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=cfad9a65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3nFFDqK</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ndUwKpq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FndUwKpq.png&h=24ed1247&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}